INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` VALUES ('3502','2','','','','0','0','','admin5','添加内容','/admin.php/cms/item-add','192.168.162.110','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'895\',\n  \'title\' => \'老干部支部举办“庆国庆、度中秋、迎重阳”系列活动\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'离退休干部处\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">在2017年国庆、中秋、重阳佳节来临之际， 10月5号市一院离退休职工“庆国庆、度中秋、迎重阳”系列活动拉开了帷幕。老干部踊跃参加，纷纷用行到表达对建国七十周年的热爱。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">王志才、张孝琴夺走了掼蛋比赛的桂冠；李德贵荣获象棋比赛的第一名；杨忠达获书画比赛第一名。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/b0d0aedb3a2c7549.png\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/be4a4bacb881ed00.png\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/70236261e9fce3dd.png\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/13d1ff4e1c4bdaba.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/a27a842be2086f61.png\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/2059ce091703a280.png\" border=\"0\"/></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'editer\' => \'[db:编辑]\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2017-10-05\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2017-10-05\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'c647986139e04712\',\n  \'views\' => \'[db:浏览量]\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'admin5\',\n  \'attribute\' => \n  array (\n    6 => 6,\n  ),\n)','1627528376');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` VALUES ('3503','2','','','','0','0','','admin5','添加内容','/admin.php/cms/item-add','192.168.162.110','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'895\',\n  \'title\' => \'老干支部组织离退休老同志参观南区\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'离退休干部处\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2017年9月19日下午，在院领导的关心下，在医院南区办公室的大力支持下，我院离退休干部处组织了部分离退休老同志参观了盐城市第一人民医院南区，让老同志实地了解医院发展的大好形 山册册势，分享医院发展成果，进一步促进老领导、老同志对医院工作的理解与支持。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/2196def87d5e4497.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">老同志们正津津有味地听办公室小罗给大家介绍医院南区的情况</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/34132621d752a147.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/f0b6f9b56b8fe7dc.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/940e2419b9c794d.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">老同志们边走边看，连连称赞我们医院南区真漂亮！医院发展真快！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/89353f76fbcfd0d5.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">老同志们在门诊药房参观了药房自动发药流程系统，直感叹高科技就是神奇！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/25a3520cbd92bd23.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/49020444bb939af0.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/7573a115c22d2b38.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">手术室护士长和消化科护士长热情地给大家介绍病区的情况，老同志们问东问西可感兴趣了。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">老同志们兴趣勃勃地追着小罗问这问那，恨不得把自己不清楚的事一下子全弄明白</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/f17bfa6eb8f99c1c.png\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/ee3b0495f2357b07.png\" border=\"0\"/></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'editer\' => \'[db:编辑]\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2017-09-19\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2017-09-19\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'6a266f4444a6695f\',\n  \'views\' => \'[db:浏览量]\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'admin5\',\n  \'attribute\' => \n  array (\n    6 => 6,\n  ),\n)','1627528376');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` VALUES ('3504','2','','','','0','0','','admin5','添加内容','/admin.php/cms/item-add','192.168.162.110','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'895\',\n  \'title\' => \'我院组织离退休老干部、老同志迎春赏游活动\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'离退休干部处\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">为丰富我院离退休干部职工的精神文化生活，受院党委的委托，我院离退休干部处及老干支部于4月18日和20日两天，分两批组织全院200多名离退休老同志赴南通如皋市水绘园、长寿园参观赏游。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">在和煦的春光中，老同志们参观了代表江南园林风格的如皋水绘园，兼具自然秀美和人文底蕴的美景给老同志留下了极其深刻的印象。通过游览，老同志们了解了历史，开阔了眼界，锻炼了身体，颐养了身心。在长寿园，大家浏览了世界最大的寿星像，祈福长寿安康。此外还组织老同志到如皋园艺馆和李昌钰刑侦博物馆赏花、参观，进一步开拓眼界。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">离退休干部处精心准备、悉心负责、考虑周全，整个参观考察活动安全顺畅愉悦，受到了广大老同志的交口称赞。此次活动的成功举办，也标志着老干部支部4月份党员活动日的一项重要内容圆满完成。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/5a7fd8f7f5d329df.jpg\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/3a985cef969b440f.jpg\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/addde6a66634f72e.jpg\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/6991b73812f2d86f.jpg\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/613163a92bec447e.jpg\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/3d3d2267df3521e7.jpg\" border=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www1.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/cfe56896c410ed64.jpg\" border=\"0\"/></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'editer\' => \'[db:编辑]\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2017-04-20\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2017-04-20\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'a99f099230c308b2\',\n  \'views\' => \'[db:浏览量]\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'admin5\',\n  \'attribute\' => \n  array (\n    6 => 6,\n  ),\n)','1627528377');
